    "text_target": "最快、最简单、最有趣的学习日语字母的方法。",
    "context": {
      "type": "language"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 24.36,
    "end": 28.84,
    "text_source": "You've learned all the 46 hiragana characters from the previous lessons.",
    "text_target": "你已经学习了前面的46个平假名字符。",
    "context": {
      "type": "language"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 28.84,
    "end": 31.4,
    "text_source": "Now, it's time to move on to katakana.",
    "text_target": "现在是时候转到片假名了。",
    "context": {
      "type": "language"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 32.84,
    "end": 35.64,
    "text_source": "In this lesson, you'll learn about katakana,",
    "text_target": "在这节课中，你将学习关于片假名的内容",
    "context": {
      "type": "language",
      "summary": "Introduction to a Japanese writing system lesson",
      "grammar": "Use of 'in this lesson' to indicate the topic",
      "cultural_note": "Katakana is a Japanese syllabary used for loanwords and emphasis",
      "vocab": [
        {
          "word": "katakana",
          "meaning": "a Japanese syllabary",
          "highlight": true
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 36.06,
    "end": 37.88,
    "text_source": "how it is different from hiragana,",
    "text_target": "它与平假名有何不同？\n\n答案：它是日语的另一套基础假名系统，主要用于表示音节和辅音。",
    "context": {
      "type": "language"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 38.32,
