  {
    "start": 0,
    "end": 13,
    "text_source": "If you have a difficult problem, you may be able to solve it by changing your way of thinking.",
    "text_target": "如果你遇到一个困难的问题，你可能通过改变自己的思维方式来解决它。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 13,
    "end": 23,
    "text_source": "I think it's the same when learning a language.",
    "text_target": "我认为学习语言也是如此。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 23,
    "end": 30.54,
    "text_source": "When we learn a new language, we find the closest pronunciation to our native language.",
    "text_target": "当我们学习一种新语言时，我们会寻找与母语最接近的发音。\n\n注：Simplified Chinese 是一种常用的中文书写形式，用于大陆中国和新加坡等地区。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 30.98,
    "end": 36.78,
    "text_source": "Even if the pronunciation is different, it is difficult for us to distinguish.",
    "text_target": "即使发音不同，我们也难以区分。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 38.8,
    "end": 42.58,
    "text_source": "So, what should we do with Chinese pronunciation?",
    "text_target": "那么，我们应该如何处理中文发音的问题？",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 45.88,
    "end": 51.34,
    "text_source": "First of all, we have to be aware that this is a pronunciation that is not in Chinese.",
    "text_target": "首先，我们必须意识到，这是一个不是汉语的发音。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 51.34,
    "end": 58.34,
    "text_source": "So, please don't pronounce it as ら in Chinese.",
    "text_target": "(Translation Failed)",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 58.34,
    "end": 60.34,
    "text_source": "I'm in trouble.",
    "text_target": "我遇到麻烦。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 60.34,
    "end": 63.34,
    "text_source": "So, how should I pronounce it?",
    "text_target": "所以，我应该如何发音？",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 63.34,
    "end": 67.34,
    "text_source": "Let's think about it the other way around.",
    "text_target": "(Translation Failed)",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 67.34,
    "end": 70.34,
    "text_source": "Let's assume that I'm a foreigner.",
    "text_target": "假设您是外国人。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 70.34,
    "end": 90.26549,
    "text_source": "No I a foreigner When I wasn very good at Chinese pronunciation I always used Japanese pronunciation For example I am Japanese",
    "text_target": "(Translation Failed)",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 90.26549,
    "end": 91.66549,
    "text_source": "Among them,",
