  },
  {
    "start": 130.26549,
    "end": 138.06549,
    "text_source": "As a result, it becomes 往事例伝 .",
    "text_target": "作为结果，它变成了往事例传。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 138.06549,
    "end": 141.06549,
    "text_source": "Now, let's get back to today's topic.",
    "text_target": "现在我们回到今天的话题。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 141.06549,
    "end": 150.8655,
    "text_source": "First, we have to listen to the difference between the Japanese ら and the Chinese ら.",
    "text_target": "首先，我们需要了解日语中的\"ら\"和中文中的\"ら\"的区别。\n\n注：由于\"ら\"在日语中的发音和中文中的发音可能不同，因此在翻译时需要注意区别。\n\n在日语中,\"ら\"通常表示\"们\"或\"们的\"的意思，例如：\n- うちら（我们）\n- うちらが（我们）\n- うちらがいる（我们在那）\n\n在中文中,\"ら\"并不是一个常见的字母或音符，可能是指其他汉字的读音或拼音，如：\n- 拉（拉）\n- 啦（啦）\n- 拉（拉）\n\n因此，在翻译时需要根据上下文确定\"ら\"的正确含义和发音。",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 150.8655,
    "end": 163.13098,
    "text_source": "Now the Japanese word is not the Chinese I think there are many people who cannot distinguish this difference",
    "text_target": "现在日本语和汉语已经不一样了，我认为有很多人无法区分这两种语言的差异。\n\n(Note: I've translated the text to Simplified Chinese, as it's the most widely used character set in mainland China, Taiwan, and other Chinese-speaking regions. If you need Traditional Chinese, please let me know.)\n\nHere's a breakdown of the translation:\n\n* \"Now\" -> \"现在\"\n* \"the Japanese word\" -> \"日本语\"\n* \"is not the Chinese\" -> \"已经不一样了\"\n* \"I think\" -> \"我认为\"\n* \"there are many people\" -> \"有很多人\"\n* \"who cannot distinguish\" -> \"无法区分\"\n* \"this difference\" -> \"这两种语言的差异\"",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 163.13098,
    "end": 167.65099,
    "text_source": "La la la la la. No matter how you listen, it's la la la la la.",
    "text_target": "(Translation Failed)",
    "context": {
      "type": "general"
    }
  },
  {
    "start": 167.65099,
    "end": 171.97098,
    "text_source": "This is because I've been thinking only in Chinese all the time.",
    "text_target": "这是因为我一直都在用中文思考。",
