    "text_target": "**计数模板**

计数模板是一种常见的模板类型，用于统计和展示数据。以下是一些常见的计数模板：

### 1. 基础计数模板

```html
<!-- 基础计数模板 -->
<div class="count">
  <span>{{ count }}</span>
  <span>个</span>
</div>
```

### 2. 增长计数模板

```html
<!-- 增长计数模板 -->
<div class="count">
  <span>{{ count }}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="growth">{{ growth }}</span>
  <span>%</span>
</div>
```

### 3. 比较计数模板

```html
<!-- 比较计数模板 -->
<div class="count">
  <span>{{ count1 }}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="compare">{{ compare }}</span>
  <span>{{ count2 }}</span>
  <span>个</span>
</div>
```

### 4. 动态计数模板

```html
<!-- 动态计数模板 -->
<div class="count">
  <span>{{ count }}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="animation">{{ animation }}</span>
</div>
```

### 使用计数模板

```javascript
// 使用计数模板
const count = 100;
const growth = 20;
const compare = 50;
const animation = 'animate';

// 基础计数模板
const basicCount = document.createElement('div');
basicCount.className = 'count';
basicCount.innerHTML = `
  <span>${count}</span>
  <span>个</span>
`;
document.body.appendChild(basicCount);

// 增长计数模板
const growthCount = document.createElement('div');
growthCount.className = 'count';
growthCount.innerHTML = `
  <span>${count}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="growth">${growth}</span>
  <span>%</span>
`;
document.body.appendChild(growthCount);

// 比较计数模板
const compareCount = document.createElement('div');
compareCount.className = 'count';
compareCount.innerHTML = `
  <span>${count1}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="compare">${compare}</span>
  <span>${count2}</span>
  <span>个</span>
`;
document.body.appendChild(compareCount);

// 动态计数模板
const dynamicCount = document.createElement('div');
dynamicCount.className = 'count';
dynamicCount.innerHTML = `
  <span>${count}</span>
  <span>个</span>
  <span class="animation">${animation}</span>
`;
document.body.appendChild(dynamicCount);
```

### 样式

```css
/* 样式 */
.count {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #333;
}

.count span {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 10px;
}

.growth {
  color: #f00;
}

.compare {
  color: #0f0;
}

.animation {
  animation: animate 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes animate {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
```

### 结论

计数模板是一种常见的模板类型，用于统计和展示数据。上述代码提供了四种常见的计数模板，包括基础计数模板、增长计数模板、比较计数模板和动态计数模板。这些模板可以根据具体需求进行定制和扩展。",
